WEBVTT

00:00:01.117 --> 00:00:05.531
Koliko ljudi ovdje bi htjelo doživjeti 
barem 80 godina?

00:00:06.072 --> 00:00:07.547
Da.

00:00:07.571 --> 00:00:10.366
Mislim da svi imamo 
ovakvo očekivanje puno nade

00:00:10.390 --> 00:00:12.350
od života u kasnoj dobi.

00:00:12.828 --> 00:00:14.914
Prebacimo se u budućnost,

00:00:14.938 --> 00:00:16.498
na vaše buduće 'vi',

00:00:16.522 --> 00:00:19.375
i zamislimo da svi imamo 85 godina.

00:00:19.894 --> 00:00:21.912
Sada neka svatko pogleda dvije osobe.

00:00:23.151 --> 00:00:26.683
Jedna od vas vjerojatno ima 
Alzheimerovu bolest.

00:00:27.365 --> 00:00:30.789
(Smijeh)